You have exceeded your premium request allowance. We have automatically switched you to GPT-4.1 which is included with your plan. [Enable additional paid premium requests](command:chat.enablePremiumOverages) to continue using premium models.```seqdiag
actor Users
boundary CapabilityProfilePage
control serviceProviderProfileController
participant ":serviceProviderProfileService" as Service
participant ":serviceProviderProfileModel" as Model
database Database

activate Users
Users->CapabilityProfilePage: 1. Click "View Capability Profile"
activate CapabilityProfilePage
CapabilityProfilePage->serviceProviderProfileController: 2. GET /service-provider-profile/capability
activate serviceProviderProfileController
serviceProviderProfileController->Service: 3. getCapabilityProfile(userId)
activate Service
Service->Model: 4. findByUserId(userId)
activate Model
Model->Database: 5. findOne()
activate Database
Database-->Model: 6. Return profile document (or null)
deactivate Database
Model-->Service: 7. Return raw result
deactivate Model
Service->Service: 8. checkQuerySuccess()
activate Service
space
deactivate Service
opt database error
    Service-->serviceProviderProfileController: 8.1 Return error
    serviceProviderProfileController-->CapabilityProfilePage: 8.2 Return error
    CapabilityProfilePage-->Users: 8.3 Display error message
else no database error
    Service->Service: 9. checkNotFound()
    activate Service
    space
    deactivate Service
    alt profile not found
        Service-->serviceProviderProfileController: 9.1 Return error: profile not found
        serviceProviderProfileController-->CapabilityProfilePage: 9.1.1 Return error
        CapabilityProfilePage-->Users: 9.1.2 Display error: profile not found
    else profile found
        Service->Service: 9.2 filterServiceAreas()
        activate Service
        space

        deactivate Service
        Service->Service: 9.3 mapToCapabilityDTO()
        activate Service
        space
        deactivate Service
        Service-->serviceProviderProfileController: 9.4 Return success + capability data
        deactivate Service
        serviceProviderProfileController-->CapabilityProfilePage: 9.5 Return success + capability data
        deactivate serviceProviderProfileController
       
        CapabilityProfilePage-->Users: 9.6 Display capability + service areas
        deactivate CapabilityProfilePage
        deactivate Users
    end
end
```